OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSummit to discuss Scottish 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffootball's pyro problem    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The increasing use of fireworks and    
OL,6, flares at Scottish football grounds is 
OL,7, to be discussed at a meeting later this
OL,8, month, BBC Scotland News has learned.  
OL,10,FIt comes after Wednesday night's match 
OL,11,Fbetween Dundee and Rangers had to be   
OL,12,Fpaused for 18 minutes after Rangers    
OL,13,Ffans let off flares in the stands.     
OL,15,FDens Park was engulfed in smoke,       
OL,16,Fsetting off a fire alarm and forcing   
OL,17,Fthe players off the pitch.             
OL,19,FThe game resumed when the smoke        
OL,20,Fcleared, with Rangers winning 5-0.     
